  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK815">
<l>ceytēmañ cārāc ciṟiyavar puṉkēṇmai</l>
<l>yeytali ṉeytāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is far better to avoid that to contract the evil friendship of the base who cannot protect (their friends) even when appointed to do so.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
